               <msContents>
                  <summary>Asmat prayer of the Archangel Mika’el, Asmat prayer of the Seven Archangels, ድርሳን፡ ዘሰባቱ፡ ሊቃነ፡ መላእክት፡</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="1r" to="14r" facs="003">Fols 1r–14r</locus>
                     <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5876AsmatPrayer">Asmat prayer of the Archangel Mika’el</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ፩ አምላክ፡ ኅቡዓተ፡ አስማቲሁ፡ ለቅዱስ፡ ሚካኤል፡ ሊቀ፡ መላእክት፡ ኤኮስ፡ አስሌ፡ ኤፓ፡ ኤፓስ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <locus from="14v" to="15v" facs="017">Fols 14v–15v</locus>
                     <title>Prayer for the Cleansing of Sin, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ መንጺሒ፡ ኃጢአት፡</foreign>
                     </title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ መንጺሒ፡ ኃጢአት፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ኩና፡ ረድኢየ፡ ለነፍስ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ኩና፡ ቀዋሚሃ፡ ለነፍስ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                     <note>written in a later hand</note>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i3">
                     <locus from="15v" to="16r" facs="018">Fols 15v–16r</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> Asmat prayer</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">Asmat prayer</incipit>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                     <note>written in faint pencil</note>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i4">
                     <locus from="17r" to="25r" facs="019">Fols 17r–25r</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> Asmat prayer of the Seven Archangels, Dǝrsanä Zäsäbatu Liqǝnä Mäla’kǝt, ድርሳን፡ ዘሰባቱ፡ ሊቃነ፡ መላእክት፡</title>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                     <note>incomplete at the beginning</note>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i4.1">
                     <locus from="17r" to="17v" facs="019">Fols 17r–17v</locus>
