                                                  mǝśṭir</title>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>

                </msItem>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i5">
                     <locus from="27r" to="31v" facs="029">Fols 27r–31v</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2927RepCh208">Malkǝʾ-hymn to St
                                                  George</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">ሰላም፡ ለጽንሰትከ፡ ወለልደትከ፡ ቡሩክ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i6">
                     <locus from="34r" to="47v" facs="036">Fols 34r–47v</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3085RepCh365">Hymn to Raguel the
                                                  Archangel</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">እጼውዕ፡ ስመከ፡ ወእኤምህ፡ በተድላ።</incipit>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i7">
                     <locus from="47v" to="47v" facs="050">Fols 47v–47v</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1097Ammest#Eucharist">ʾAmmǝstu
                                                  ʾaʿǝmāda mǝśṭir, Mystery of the Eucharist (ምሥጢረ፡
                                                  ቍርባን፡)</title>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i8">
                     <locus from="47v" to="47v" facs="050"> f. 47v, upper</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1097Ammest#Resurrection">ʾAmmǝstu ʾaʿǝmāda mǝśṭir, Mystery ofthe
                                                  Resurrection (ምሥጢረ፡ ትንሣኤ፡)</title>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                     <note>Begins 47v</note>
                  </msItem>
